k Liberty own the league's best record (21-4) and sit 2.5 games ahead of the second-place Connecticut Sun.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Liberty\", \"score\": 0.999999987361207, \"rank\": 1.2372402374091066e-08, \"text\": \"New York Liberty\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Liberty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Liberty\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut_Sun\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.379930007783813e-13, \"text\": \"Connecticut Sun\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut_Sun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut_Sun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Liberty, who also have thehighest net rating(11.8), are a strong bet to stay there as long as their key players stay healthy.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plenty of drama remains regarding the rest of the playoff bracket.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only 0.5 games separate the third-place Minnesota Lynx from the Seattle Storm in fifth, while the gap between sixth and eight place is only 2.5 games.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the last-place Dallas Wings can not be totally overlooked because a hot stretch could help them close their 3.5-game difference on the Sky for the final postseason berth.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas_Wings\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 4.174939539002651e-12, \"text\": \"Dallas Wings\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas_Wings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.